00:00:07.300 --> 00:00:10.300
 Chinese braised pork 

00:00:13.600 --> 00:00:17.600
 Cooking ingredients: 1 / 2kg of coconut juice fresh, bacon, 2 tbsp thick soy sauce, 2 tbsp sugar, 

00:00:18.800 --> 00:00:25.800
 1 tbsp rock sugar, 1tsp salt, 1/2 tbsp fish sauce, 1-2 star anise, minced garlic and onion 

00:00:28.500 --> 00:00:36.593
 Bring a pot of water to a boil. Blanch the pork for 5 minutes. This gets rid of impurities and starts the cooking process. Take the pork out of the pot and set aside. Bạn có thể xử lý gà trước hoặc sau sau này 

00:00:41.900 --> 00:00:55.900
 Over low heat, add oil and 2 tbsp sugar to your pan 

00:01:00.500 --> 00:01:06.573
 Melt the sugar slightly and add the pork. The heat to medium and cook until the pork is lightly browned 

00:01:11.900 --> 00:01:16.900
 Mix well salt + fish sauce into pan 

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:34.054
 Then add 1/2 bowl coconut juice and 2 star anises 

00:01:38.300 --> 00:01:40.300
 Cover and simmer for about 30 minutes 

00:01:41.900 --> 00:01:47.900
 The sauce is dry but pork is not folk tender, add the then juice coconut rest 

00:01:49.600 --> 00:01:59.600
 When pork is folk tender, add more rock sugar to make the sauce has a glistening coating 

